15,01So I seem to fall eternally.

15,01Black Hole Soul,
15,01It's my goal;
15,01Dark as coal,
15,01Black Hole Soul.

15,01Pain within me, something dies;
15,01I've lost my life to all my lies.
15,01Sell my soul to quiet the cries,
15,01But demons still scream within my eyes.

15,01Black Hole Soul,
